"|<notr>Otchocut</notr>|Great fish|Delphinus|\n"
"|<notr>Porkelong toute</notr>|Loss of tooth|Shooting star|\n"
"|<notr>Pupperimbul</notr>|Diamond firetail finch or shy hylacola|Carried the "
